      <title>Factorio Beacon and Module Guide - 8-Beacon Layout and Optimization</title>
      <link>https://factorioguides.com/production-ratios/beacon-module-guide/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 May 2026 16:52:00 +0800</pubDate>
