      <description>&lt;p&gt;Beacons amplify module effects across multiple buildings. &lt;span class=&#34;mat-card&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://factorioguides.com/images/icon/beacon.png&#34; alt=&#34;beacon&#34; class=&#34;mat-card-img&#34; title=&#34;Beacon&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;span class=&#34;mat-name&#34;&gt;Beacon&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA; One beacon with &lt;span class=&#34;mat-card&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://factorioguides.com/images/icon/productivity_module_3.png&#34; alt=&#34;productivity_module_3&#34; class=&#34;mat-card-img&#34; title=&#34;Productivity&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;span class=&#34;mat-name&#34;&gt;Productivity&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA; speed modules can boost 8 nearby assemblers --if you lay them out correctly.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;pro-tip&#34;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;TL;DR:&lt;/strong&gt; 8-beacon layout surrounds one assembler with 8 beacons. Fill beacons with speed modules, assemblers with productivity modules. Result: +30% productivity at +10% speed. The endgame standard for expensive recipes.&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;img src=&#34;https://factorioguides.com/images/diagrams/8-beacon-layout.svg&#34; alt=&#34;8-beacon layout showing assembler surrounded by 8 beacons with module distribution&#34; class=&#34;schema-diagram&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; width=&#34;900&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;how-beacons-work&#34;&gt;How Beacons Work&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Beacons transmit module effects to nearby buildings:&lt;/p&gt;</description>
